  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <head>Cēṉāvaraiyar</head>
        <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Ci. Vai. Tamōtarampiḷḷai</persName> 1868, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n70/mode/1up">67</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n71/mode/1up">68</ref>.</p>
      <p>i - ḷ. peyarum peyaruntokka tokaiyumuḷa; avaiyumuriya eḻuvāyvēṟṟumaiyāyppayaṉilai kōṭaṟku. e - ṟu.</p>
<p>u-m. yāṉaikkōṭu kiṭantatu; matimukam viyarttatu; kolyāṉai niṉṟatu; karuṅkutirai yōṭiṟṟu; uvāppatiṉāṉku kaḻintaṉa; poṟṟoṭi vantāḷ eṉa varum.</p>
<p>peyariṉākiya tokaiyumeṉṉu mummaiyāl, peyaroṭupeyar tokkaṉavēyaṉṟi, nilaṅkiṭantāṉ; mākkoṇarntāṉ eṉap peyaroṭu viṉai vantu tokka viṉaiyiṉākiya tokaiyumuḷaveṉpatām. ākavē, peyaroṭu peyarum peyaroṭu toḻilun tokkaṉa tokaiyeṉpatu peṟṟām.</p>
<p>avvumuriyaveṉap potuvakaiyāṟ kūṟiṉārēṉum, ēṟpuḻik kōṭaleṉpataṉāṉ eḻuvāy vēṟṟumaiyātaṟ kēṟpuṭaiya peyariṉākiya tokaiyē koḷḷappaṭum.</p>
<p>irutoṭarpaṭaccūttirittiṭarppaṭuvateṉṉai? peyariṉākiya tokaiyum eḻuvāyvēṟṟumaiyāmeṉṟōtavamaiyātōveṉiṉ:- aṅṅaṉamōtiṟ peyaroṭu peyarum peyaroṭu viṉaiyun tokkaṉa tokaiccollāmeṉṉun tokaiyilakkaṇam peṟappaṭātām; avvilakkaṇa muṇarttutaṟku ivvāṟu pirittōtiṉāreṉpatu.</p>
<p>peyariṉākiya tokaiyumeṉṟavummaiyāṉ viṉaiyiṉākiya viṉaittokai taḻuvappaṭṭateṉṟum, "ellāt tokaiyu morucoṉ ṉaṭaiya" eṉpataṉāl tokaiccollellām eḻuvāyvēṟṟumaiyātal peṟappaṭutaliṉ, īṇṭu avvumuriyavappālāṉaveṉṟatu tokaiccoṟkuppayaṉilai kōṭaṉmāttira meytuvittaṟkeṉṟum, uraiyāciriyar kūṟiṉārāleṉiṉ:- aṟṟaṉṟu: viṉaittokaikku nilaimoḻi viṉaiyeṉpatu uraiyāciriyarkkuk karuttaṉmai "viṉaiyiṉ ṟokuti kālat tiyalum" eṉṉuñ cūttirattiṟ collutum. iṉi "ellāt tokaiyu morucoṉ ṉaṭaiya" eṉpataṟku orucoṉṉaṭaiyavāmeṉpatallatu eḻuvāyvēṟṟumaiyāmeṉṉuṅ karuttiṉmaiyāṉum, akkaruttuṇṭāyiṉ avaiyum eḻuvāyvēṟṟumaiyāy niṉṟu "aṉṟi yaṉaittum peyarppaya ṉilaiyē" eṉṟataṉāṟ payaṉilaiyeytumākaliṉ avvumuriyavappālāṉaveṉṟal kūṟiyatu kūṟiṟṟāmākalāṉum, atuvumuraiyāciriyar karuttaṉṟeṉka.</p>
<p>aḵtēl, tokaiyum eḻuvāyvēṟṟumaiyāmeṉpatē iccūttirattiṟkuk karuttāyiṉ "eḻuvāy vēṟṟumai peyartōṉṟu nilaiyē" eṉṉuñ cūttirattiṉpiṉ vaikkaveṉiṉ;- peyar tōṉṟiya tuṇaiyāy niṟṟalum payaṉilaikōṭalumākiya eḻuvāyvēṟṟumai yilakkaṇamiraṇṭun tokaiccoṟku meytuvittaṟku avviraṇṭu cūttirattiṟkum piṉ vaittāreṉpatu. āṇṭu vaippiṉ, "aṉṟi yaṉaittum peyarppaya ṉilaiyē" eṉṟataṉāṟ payaṉilaikōṭal peyarkkēyāyat tokaikkeytātā meṉpatu.	(6)</p>
    </body>
